UNITED STATES ex rel. William BOBKOWSKI, Relator-Appellant, v. Henry H. CURRAN, as Commissioner, etc., Respondent-Appellee. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. October 7, 1926.) No. 21. Robert Spear, of New York City, for appellant. Emory R. Buckner, U. S. Atty., of New York City (Nathan R. Margold, Asst. U. S. Atty., of New York City, of counsel), for appellee. '

Before HOUGH, MANTON, and HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed in open court.
